messages.msgSnippet: We have two close by here.  The kidlets want to go to the goat cheese farm because we buy the cheese and goat sausage at the farmers market and it rarely lasts
messages.messageBody:
We have two close by here. The kidlets want to go to the goat cheese farm
because we buy the cheese and goat sausage at the farmers market and it
rarely lasts more than a day or two!

The other cheese factory also does organic cheeses and the aged cheddar is
absolutely to die for!!!!

Lynda
